msgctxt "92_Tanimura"
msgid "Saki-chan, are you all right?"
msgstr "¿Te encuentras bien, Saki-chan?"

msgctxt "104_Saki-chan"
msgid "*pant* Whew! *pant* I haven't ran that much in ages!"
msgstr "*Jadeos* ¡Uf! *Jadeos* ¡Hace siglos que no corría así!"

msgctxt "116_Tanimura"
msgid "Oh, you'll live. Now where's Tsugawa's company, this \"Urban Foods\"? I'm going after him."
msgstr "Oh, Estarás Bien. Ahora, ¿dónde está la empresa de Tsugawa, esta \"Urban Foods\"? Voy tras él."

msgctxt "128_Saki-chan"
msgid "Don't you think you're rushing things just a bit?"
msgstr "¿No crees que te estás apresurando un poco?"

msgctxt "140_Tanimura"
msgid "We've already been targeted by hitmen. If we don't act fast, we'll only be leaving ourselves open to more danger. It's time to go on the offensive."
msgstr "Los sicarios ya nos tienen en la mira. Si no nos movemos rápido, solo les vamos a dar más ventaja. Es hora de pasar a la ofensiva."

msgctxt "152_Saki-chan"
msgid "There's that youthful optimism shining through..."
msgstr "El típico optimismo de los jóvenes..."

msgctxt "164_Saki-chan"
msgid "All right. Urban Foods is in the building with the information booth on Suppon Street. Don't take them lightly."
msgstr "Está bien. Urban Foods está en el edificio con el puesto de información en Suppon Street. No los subestimes."

msgctxt "176_Tanimura"
msgid "Suppon Street. Got it."
msgstr "Suppon Street. Recibido."

